    <section class="management" id="management">
    	<div class="content">
        <h1>Specialized Management of Planning, Design &amp; Construction</h1>
	    	<p>In collaboration with our key partner, California-based Lean Engineering, we help create, improve and validate master plans, designs and construction phasing plans so no detail is overlooked. Our unique access to Air Carrier, USAF, NGA and FAA technology allows us to simulate or emulate calculations from any stakeholder's perspective before, during or after the typical planning or design process.</p>
        <p>Learn More at <a target="blank" href="http://leancorp.com/">Leancorp.com</a></p>
