              <div class="content">
                <h3>Paul Hannah</h3>
                <h4><strong>President &amp; Chief Engineer</strong><br>Atlanta, GA UTC -5 (-4)</h4>
                <div class="column">
                  <p>
                    Paul Hannah is the President and Chief Engineer for DragonFly Aeronautics, LLC. In his role, Paul is responsible for managing the strategic vision, operations, business development, consulting service provision and engineering solutions.
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    As a senior executive with 16 years of experience in Aviation and Flight Operations Engineering, Hannah works to ensure that DragonFly software and services support the complex and dynamic demands of the aviation industry.
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    As Chief Engineer for DragonFly, Hannah develops and delivers consulting engineering services for aircraft performance engineering, flight operations engineering, airport planning/design/construction, flight safety and regulatory compliance.
                  </p>
                </div>
